ReportBundle.ReportXML: <Report ReportGID="3efc40dc-b5a7-46f0-890d-d715c396b201" ReportUseType="2" ReportType="5" ReportName="Pens by Daily DMI with Weighback" Description="Crosstab of Pen's Daily Dry Matter Intake including Weighbacks" CreatedDT="2013-11-14T09:06:23.557" ModifiedDT="2014-05-19T17:18:00.62" ModifiedBy="VAS" ConcurrencyTS="AAAAAAAAK/I=" ReportVersion="0" />

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText:
<QueryBundle> <QueryText>select cmp.CompanyName ,pn.PenGID ,pt.PenTypeName ,z.ReportDate ,pn.PenNumber ,pl.LocationName as 'PenName' ,z.AvgPenCount ,z.WAvgPenCount ,z.BackupPenCount ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.DropAFOz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'DropAF' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.DropAFOzHd, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'DropAFHd' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.DropDMOz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'DropDM' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.DropDMOzHd, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'DropDMHd' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.PickupAFOz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'PickupAF' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ISNULL(z.PickupAFOz / NULLIF(z.WAvgPenCount, 0), 0.0), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'PickupAFHd' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.PickupDMOz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'PickupDM' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ISNULL(z.PickupDMOz / NULLIF(z.WAvgPenCount, 0), 0.0), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'PickupDMHd' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.WBDropAFOz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'WBDropAF' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ISNULL(z.WBDropAFOz / NULLIF(z.WAvgPenCount, 0), 0.0), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'WBDropAFHd' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.WBDropDMOz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'WBDropDM' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ISNULL(z.WBDropDMOz / NULLIF(z.WAvgPenCount, 0), 0.0), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'WBDropDMHd' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.TotalAFOz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TotalAF' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ISNULL(z.TotalAFOz / NULLIF(z.WAvgPenCount, 0), 0.0), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TotalAFHd' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(z.TotalDMOz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TotalDM' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(ISNULL(z.TotalDMOz / NULLIF(z.WAvgPenCount, 0), 0.0), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TotalDMHd' from ( select pen_days.PenGID ,pen_days.ReportDate ,pen_day_drop.AvgPenCount ,pen_day_drop.DropAFOz ,pen_day_drop.DropAFOzHd ,pen_day_drop.DropDMOz ,pen_day_drop.DropDMOzHd ,ISNULL( pen_day_pickup.PickupAFOz, 0.0 ) as 'PickupAFOz' ,ISNULL( pen_day_pickup.PickupDMOz, 0.0 ) as 'PickupDMOz' ,ISNULL( pen_day_wb_drop.WBDropAFOz, 0.0) as 'WBDropAFOz' ,ISNULL( pen_day_wb_drop.WBDropDMOz, 0.0) as 'WBDropDMOz' ,pen_day_pickup.BackupPenCount ,ISNULL( pen_day_drop.DropAFOz, 0.0) + ISNULL( pen_day_pickup.PickupAFOz, 0.0 ) + ISNULL(pen_day_wb_drop.WBDropAFOz, 0.0) as 'TotalAFOz' ,ISNULL( pen_day_drop.DropDMOz, 0.0) + ISNULL( pen_day_pickup.PickupDMOz, 0.0 ) + ISNULL(pen_Day_wb_drop.WBDropDMOz, 0.0) as 'TotalDMOz' ,coalesce(pen_day_drop.DropDMOz / NULLIF(pen_day_drop.DropDMOzHd, 0), pen_day_pickup.BackupPenCount, 0.0) as 'WAvgPenCount' from ( select fs.InstanceDate as 'ReportDate' ,pn.PenGID from FeedingSchedule fs join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleGID = fs.FeedingScheduleGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingScheduleDrop fsd on fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join Pen pn on pn.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID where exists (select 1 from InventoryTransaction where TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID) group by pn.PenGID, fs.InstanceDate
union
select CONVERT(DATE, DATEADD(SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT)) as 'ReportDate' ,pn.PenGID from InventoryTransaction it join Pen pn on pn.LocationGID = it.FromLocationGID where it.TransactionType = 6
) pen_days
outer apply ( select pn.PenGID ,fs.InstanceDate as 'ReportDate' ,CONVERT(REAL, AVG(pcc.[Count])) as 'AvgPenCount' ,SUM(drop_trans.AFOz) as 'DropAFOz' ,SUM(ISNULL(drop_trans.AFOz / NULLIF(pcc.[Count], 0), 0.0)) as 'DropAFOzHd' ,SUM(drop_trans.DMOz) as 'DropDMOz' ,SUM(ISNULL(drop_trans.DMOz / NULLIF(pcc.[Count], 0), 0.0)) as 'DropDMOzHd' from FeedingSchedule fs join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleGID = fs.FeedingScheduleGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingScheduleDrop fsd on fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join Pen pn on pn.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID join ( select it.TransactionSourceGID ,DATEADD( SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT ) as 'StartDT' ,SUM( it.UnitQuantity ) as 'AFOz' ,SUM( it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct ) as 'DMOz' from InventoryTransaction it where it.TransactionType in (1,5) group by it.TransactionSourceGID, it.TransactionDT, it.DurationSeconds ) drop_trans on drop_trans.TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID left join PenCountChange pcc on pcc.PenCountChangeGID = (select top 1 pcc2.PenCountChangeGID from PenCountChange pcc2 where pcc2.PenGID = pn.PenGID and pcc2.InventoryItemType = 3 and pcc2.CreatedDT <= drop_trans.StartDT order by pcc2.CreatedDT desc) where fs.InstanceDate = pen_days.ReportDate and pn.PenGID = pen_days.PenGID group by fs.InstanceDate, pn.PenGID ) pen_day_drop
outer apply ( select pn.PenGID ,ReportDate = CONVERT( DATE, DATEADD( SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT )) --CONVERT( date, DATEADD(day, case when convert(time, dateadd(second, -it.durationseconds, it.TransactionDT)) < cmp.DayStartTime then -2 else -1 end, DATEADD(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT))) ,BackupPenCount = pcc.[Count] ,PickupAFOz = SUM(-it.UnitQuantity) ,PickupDMOz = SUM(-it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct) from InventoryTransaction it join Pen pn on pn.LocationGID = it.FromLocationGID join Location dl on dl.LocationGID = it.FromLocationGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = dl.CompanyGID join PenCountChange pcc on pcc.PenCountChangeGID = (select top 1 pcc2.PenCountChangeGID from PenCountChange pcc2 where pcc2.PenGID = pn.PenGID and pcc2.InventoryItemType = 3 and pcc2.CreatedDT <= CONVERT( DATE, DATEADD( SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT )) order by pcc2.CreatedDT desc) where it.TransactionType = 6 and pn.PenGID = pen_days.PenGID and CONVERT( DATE, DATEADD( SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT )) = pen_days.ReportDate --CONVERT( date, DATEADD(day, case when convert(time, dateadd(second, -it.durationseconds, it.TransactionDT)) < cmp.DayStartTime then -2 else -1 end, DATEADD(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT))) = pen_days.ReportDate group by pn.PenGID, CONVERT( DATE, DATEADD( SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT )), pcc.[Count] --CONVERT( date, DATEADD(day, case when convert(time, dateadd(second, -it.durationseconds, it.TransactionDT)) < cmp.DayStartTime then -2 else -1 end, DATEADD(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT))) ) pen_day_pickup
outer apply ( select pn.PenGID ,ReportDate = CONVERT( DATE, DATEADD( SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT)) ,WBDropAFOz = SUM(it.UnitQuantity) ,WBDropDMOz = SUM(it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct) from InventoryTransaction it join ManualFeeding mf on mf.ManualFeedingGID = it.TransactionSourceGID join Location tl on tl.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = tl.CompanyGID join Pen pn on pn.LocationGID = tl.LocationGID where it.TransactionType = 1 and pn.PenGID = pen_days.PenGID and CONVERT( DATE, DATEADD(SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT)) = pen_days.ReportDate group by pn.PenGID, CONVERT( DATE, DATEADD(SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT)) ) pen_day_wb_drop
) z join Pen pn on pn.PenGID = z.PenGID join Location pl on pl.LocationGID = pn.LocationGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = pl.CompanyGID join PenType pt on pt.PenTypeGID = (select top 1 ppt.PenTypeGID from PenPenType ppt where ppt.PenGID = pn.PenGID and ppt.IsPrimary = 1 and ppt.Inactive = 0)
where (1=1)</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
